# Claude Code local permission cache. Records approved commands verbatim, which
# has included AWIN datafeed URLs with AWIN_API_KEY inline. That key cannot be
# rotated on our account, so this must never be committed. Previously only
# covered by a machine-global ~/.config/git/ignore, which a fresh clone lacks.
